BT
/F2 16 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 820.00 Tm
(Resume Writer App Summary) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 794.00 Tm
(What it is) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 776.00 Tm
(Flask-backed web tool that rewrites curated sample resumes to mirror a provided job description by coordinating with OpenRouter/DeepSeek and producing a browser-printable HTML/PDF output.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 760.00 Tm
(Who it is for) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 742.00 Tm
(Career coaches or job seekers who need to transform an existing resume into a JD-focused pitch without manually crafting every bullet point.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 726.00 Tm
(What it does) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 708.00 Tm
(- Hosts resumes in JSON under resumes/ and exposes a sample picker plus listing APIs for automation.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 693.50 Tm
(- Collects job descriptions through the React-like form in templates/index.html and posts them to /generate.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 679.00 Tm
(- Logs each JD with timestamps under logs/ while deriving company names for file naming.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 664.50 Tm
(- Calls OpenAI DeepSeek via OpenRouter to rewrite the selected sample into a JD-aligned structure.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 650.00 Tm
(- Sanitizes and styles the rewritten JSON as HTML and saves the document under outputs/ for preview/print.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 635.50 Tm
(- Serves the HTML resume for live preview and lets the browser print or download PDFs.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 621.00 Tm
(- Offers simple APIs \(samples, sample/<name>, view/<filename>\) for automation or integration.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 606.50 Tm
(How it works) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 588.50 Tm
(templates/index.html renders the form, sample picker, and preview iframe while DOMPurify keeps previews safe.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 572.50 Tm
(Client-side JS posts JSON payloads to Flask's /generate endpoint; the app loads a sample resume JSON, validates the JD, logs it, and calls DeepSeek via the OpenAI client.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 556.50 Tm
(DeepSeek returns sanitized resume JSON, json_to_html formats it, and the result is written to outputs/ for preview/print.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 540.50 Tm
(/view/<filename> and /samples expose stored HTML and sample metadata so integrations or the browser can re-render without re-running DeepSeek.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
1 0 0 1 40.00 524.50 Tm
(How to run) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 506.50 Tm
(- source ./venv/bin/activate \(or let run.sh bootstrap the venv\)) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 492.00 Tm
(- pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 52.00 477.50 Tm
(- python app.py \(or ./run.sh to set up the venv + launch Flask at http://localhost:8080\)) Tj
ET
